summary: An ordinance appropriating the sum of $25.00 out of the general fund to the City of Seattle to pay the claim of Selinda S. Hewitt and W. M. Hewitt, her husband, for damage to real property, viz., grass, shrubbery and ornamental bushes and trees on property described as lot 11, block 2, Observatory Addition to the City of Seattle, on the 24th day of August 1917, and authorizing the drawing of a warrant therefor.
